Package: nemeton
Type: Package
Title: Systemic Forest Analysis Using the Nemeton Method
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pascal", "Obstétar", email = "pascal.obstetar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Implement the Nemeton method for systemic forest territory analysis.
    Calculate multi-family biophysical indicators across 12 ecosystem service
    families (carbon, water, soil, landscape, biodiversity, etc.), perform
    temporal analysis, normalize to composite indices, and visualize results.
    Designed for foresters, ecologists, and land managers.
